ZH: 未定之天，风雨难料。
EN: The future is unpredictable, storms may come.

ZH: 未定之天，愿我们都平安无事。
EN: In the uncertain future, may we all be safe and sound.

ZH: 未定之天，让我们继续努力前行。
EN: In the unknown future, let us continue to strive forward.

ZH: 未定之天，希望我们的愿望都能实现。
EN: In the yet to be determined future, may all our wishes come true.

