EN: In the uncertain future, everyone has a responsibility to work towards their own future.

ZH: 未定之天，正是展现自己决心的时刻。
EN: In the undecided future, it's a time to show determination.

ZH: 未定之天，别放弃对美好的追求。
EN: In the uncertain future, don't give up on pursuing what is good.

